title: Georgia Tech's Kauf, Notre Dame's Holloway Claim ACC Softball Weekly Honors - The ACC
content: Georgia Tech's Kauf, Notre Dame's Holloway Claim ACC Softball Weekly Honors  The ACC
description: GREENSBORO, N.C. (theACC.com) – Georgia Tech junior catcher Emma Kauf has been named the Atlantic Coast Conference Softball Player of the Week, while Notre Dame’s Alexis Holloway earned ACC Pitcher of the Week honors.
